#: ../pro/2fa-google.rst:10
msgid ""
"Go to `https://myaccount.google.com/security#signin <https://myaccount."
"google.com/intro/security>`_"
msgstr ""
"Μεταβείτε στη διεύθυνση `https://myaccount.google.com/security#signin "
