#: ../pro/linux/disk-encryption-luks.rst:8
msgid ""
"This guide shows how to configure LUKS-encrypted volumes, to authenticate at "
"boot with `Nitrokey Pro <https://shop.nitrokey.com/shop/product/nk-pro-2-"
